WEBVTT

00:00:12.839 --> 00:00:14.019
Zhu Helai.

00:00:15.580 --> 00:00:16.820
Zhu Helai...

00:00:20.339 --> 00:00:25.100
Wait, what reason could he have
to take Guangcai away like that?

00:00:25.260 --> 00:00:26.320
What reason?

00:00:27.100 --> 00:00:29.472
Zhu Helai was assigned
to work in the cafeteria long ago.

00:00:30.260 --> 00:00:32.359
Logically,
he shouldn't investigate any case.

00:00:33.380 --> 00:00:34.912
Today, he could lead the team

00:00:35.488 --> 00:00:38.780
and take Guangcai
from the group's IPO banquet.

00:00:40.219 --> 00:00:41.960
He might have some evidence.

00:00:52.840 --> 00:00:53.420
Lijun.

00:00:58.380 --> 00:01:01.140
Could it because...

00:01:06.379 --> 00:01:07.159
Don't panic.

00:01:08.739 --> 00:01:09.780
Old matters.

00:01:11.099 --> 00:01:12.280
It's time to sort them out.

00:02:21.280 --> 00:02:24.000
=The Silent Rift=

00:02:24.256 --> 00:02:26.984
=Episode 2=
(I Confess)

00:02:47.560 --> 00:02:50.580
The chairman of the listed company
really has strong mental fortitude.

00:02:51.240 --> 00:02:55.240
Master, once you left the interrogation
room, he clammed up again.

00:02:57.620 --> 00:02:58.860
He's putting on a show there.

00:02:59.680 --> 00:03:01.740
On the surface, he seems peaceful.

00:03:02.680 --> 00:03:04.180
But inside, he's already in turmoil.

00:03:05.560 --> 00:03:06.400
Why?

00:03:06.580 --> 00:03:10.460
He still doesn't know
why we brought him in.

00:03:11.080 --> 00:03:12.580
He's waiting for us to make the move.

00:03:13.960 --> 00:03:16.620
Fine, let him guess.

00:03:17.020 --> 00:03:18.300
Take the edge off him.

00:03:19.900 --> 00:03:20.520
Master.

00:03:21.060 --> 00:03:23.900
We brought him in
based on his son's blood sample.

00:03:24.300 --> 00:03:26.800
But the official comparison results
will take seven days.

00:03:27.139 --> 00:03:28.560
You know the detention time.

00:03:28.560 --> 00:03:29.240
Once it's up,

00:03:29.240 --> 00:03:31.139
even if he says nothing,
we have to let him go.

00:03:34.419 --> 00:03:37.900
Tomorrow, confirm with Chief Liu
to extend the investigation time.

00:03:40.448 --> 00:03:42.400
(Summoned for investigation
for 12 hours)

00:03:47.424 --> 00:03:50.752
(Xue Yonghui, Xue Qin's younger brother)

00:03:53.240 --> 00:03:53.919
Qin.

00:03:54.020 --> 00:03:55.340
Xiaoliang hasn't come home yet.

00:03:55.580 --> 00:03:57.620
I asked several classmates,
and none have seen him.

00:03:58.020 --> 00:03:59.460
With such a big thing happening,

00:03:59.919 --> 00:04:02.460
he must be upset
and went out for a walk.

00:04:02.740 --> 00:04:05.199
Xiaoliang is grown up.
He should be back soon.

00:04:05.680 --> 00:04:06.919
But you...

00:04:07.120 --> 00:04:09.800
Don't worry about me.
I'm just a bit tired.

00:04:10.080 --> 00:04:12.340
It's late. You should go home and rest.

00:04:37.620 --> 00:04:38.540
Someone's fighting.

00:04:38.540 --> 00:04:39.060
Come now.

00:04:39.060 --> 00:04:39.819
Let me see.

00:04:39.840 --> 00:04:40.800
(Liang Huifen, Zhu Helai's wife)

00:04:43.819 --> 00:04:45.879
It's my husband!

00:04:52.519 --> 00:04:53.860
- The cops!
- The cops!

00:04:55.480 --> 00:04:56.920
- Call the cops!
- Leave!

00:05:05.500 --> 00:05:07.040
On our first date,

00:05:07.040 --> 00:05:08.540
you got into a fight with some punks.

00:05:08.660 --> 00:05:10.540
After many years,
you are still doing so?

00:05:10.540 --> 00:05:11.240
Alright.

00:05:11.240 --> 00:05:12.680
What have you done?

00:05:14.300 --> 00:05:15.920
It happened in front of my supermarket.

00:05:16.100 --> 00:05:17.240
What if it didn't?

00:05:17.980 --> 00:05:18.800
Stop nagging.

00:05:20.060 --> 00:05:21.480
I am just worried about you.

00:05:21.660 --> 00:05:23.660
Qianqian is home.
Don't talk about it at home.

00:05:35.420 --> 00:05:36.180
Zhu.

00:05:38.860 --> 00:05:40.000
I knew you'd come,

00:05:41.259 --> 00:05:42.560
but I didn't expect it so soon.

00:05:43.500 --> 00:05:44.160
Come in.

00:05:45.920 --> 00:05:46.500
Hello, Huifen.

00:05:46.500 --> 00:05:47.300
Xue Qin.

00:05:47.600 --> 00:05:48.360
Hello, ma'am.

00:05:48.759 --> 00:05:50.060
Qianqian is so tall now.

00:05:50.480 --> 00:05:51.100
So pretty.

00:05:51.100 --> 00:05:51.920
Have you eaten?

00:05:51.920 --> 00:05:53.660
- I've eaten.
- Have some.

00:05:53.660 --> 00:05:55.040
- I'll change my shoes.
- No need.

00:05:55.240 --> 00:05:55.980
It is messy here.

00:05:55.980 --> 00:05:56.980
No need. Come in and sit.

00:05:56.980 --> 00:05:57.800
Not messy at all.

00:05:57.800 --> 00:05:58.560
Come in and sit.

00:05:59.040 --> 00:06:00.240
How clean this place is.

00:06:00.620 --> 00:06:01.860
Let me get you some water.

00:06:01.920 --> 00:06:03.040
No need. I'll do it myself.

00:06:03.040 --> 00:06:03.680
Just wait.

00:06:05.180 --> 00:06:05.680
Here.

00:06:08.060 --> 00:06:09.120
Okay, then you chat.

00:06:19.860 --> 00:06:21.360
Just say what you have to say.

00:06:22.860 --> 00:06:23.720
Zhu.

00:06:24.860 --> 00:06:27.680
All these years,
you've been supporting Meng

00:06:28.100 --> 00:06:29.220
and helped him a lot.

00:06:29.660 --> 00:06:33.660
The friendship between you two
is more than anything.

00:06:34.420 --> 00:06:35.420
I know Guangcai.

00:06:36.500 --> 00:06:39.660
In his heart, he's always regarded you
as his big brother.

00:06:41.060 --> 00:06:43.040
Don't let reporters hear that.

00:06:43.740 --> 00:06:47.180
Otherwise, they will
make headlines out of it.

00:06:47.180 --> 00:06:49.240
Those news reports are all fake.

00:06:50.800 --> 00:06:52.860
But the friendship
between you two is real.

00:07:12.360 --> 00:07:13.800
Running the business is exhausting.

00:07:14.860 --> 00:07:17.980
In recent years, his health hasn't been
as good. He always has insomnia

00:07:18.920 --> 00:07:20.480
and terrible headaches.

00:07:20.860 --> 00:07:22.160
I always advise him

00:07:22.600 --> 00:07:25.000
to leave business matters alone.

00:07:26.160 --> 00:07:27.456
But he didn't listen to me.

00:07:28.360 --> 00:07:30.259
A clear conscience
makes for a broad horizon.

00:07:32.240 --> 00:07:33.800
If he hasn't done anything guilty,

00:07:34.540 --> 00:07:35.680
he can sleep peacefully.

00:07:39.100 --> 00:07:41.660
Caisheng Group has grown
to its current size,

00:07:42.420 --> 00:07:43.540
with numerous shareholders.

00:07:44.360 --> 00:07:46.800
The interests involved
are extremely complex.

00:07:47.160 --> 00:07:48.759
As the chairman,

00:07:50.300 --> 00:07:51.680
Guangcai might be targeted.

00:07:52.360 --> 00:07:54.240
Others might not know about it,

00:07:54.540 --> 00:07:56.100
but I bet you know.

00:07:59.660 --> 00:08:01.660
This time, Meng Guangcai
has been brought in by us,

00:08:02.160 --> 00:08:04.360
and until a conclusion is reached,
nothing is certain.

00:08:04.660 --> 00:08:07.040
Whether it's him or Caisheng Group,

00:08:07.300 --> 00:08:08.860
as long as they abide by the law,

00:08:09.860 --> 00:08:12.120
the law won't wrong any innocent person.

00:08:13.920 --> 00:08:15.860
I'm not here
with any ulterior motive today.

00:08:17.360 --> 00:08:18.800
He left in quite a hurry,

00:08:19.360 --> 00:08:21.480
and forgot to bring
his regular medication.

00:08:21.480 --> 00:08:23.800
Please pass these on to him.

00:08:24.560 --> 00:08:26.980
We are closely monitoring
his health condition.

00:08:26.980 --> 00:08:28.352
Me accepting these items

00:08:30.048 --> 00:08:31.360
violates protocol.

00:08:32.299 --> 00:08:33.539
Please take them back.

00:08:34.360 --> 00:08:36.480
Okay, I understand.

00:08:37.799 --> 00:08:39.179
I shouldn't cause you any trouble.

00:08:41.419 --> 00:08:43.639
I'm off now.

00:08:46.860 --> 00:08:47.480
Xue Qin.

00:08:49.440 --> 00:08:50.720
I understand how you feel,

00:08:52.200 --> 00:08:53.940
but it's best to keep a low profile.

00:08:55.240 --> 00:08:57.480
No matter what the media reports say,

00:08:58.639 --> 00:08:59.639
it won't help him.

00:09:08.759 --> 00:09:11.639
Your son Xiaoliang
hasn't been in the best health.

00:09:12.759 --> 00:09:13.700
Take care of him

00:09:14.600 --> 00:09:15.980
and try to calm him down.

00:09:17.820 --> 00:09:18.820
I understand.

00:09:21.440 --> 00:09:22.500
Thank you, Zhu.

00:10:04.976 --> 00:10:06.432
(Lijun)

00:10:08.740 --> 00:10:12.379
Sorry, the subscriber you dialed
is currently unavailable.

00:10:12.480 --> 00:10:13.840
Please try again later.

00:10:22.639 --> 00:10:24.620
You haven't eaten a bite.

00:10:25.960 --> 00:10:26.500
No need.

00:10:26.500 --> 00:10:27.200
Just a bite.

00:10:27.200 --> 00:10:28.580
No, I have no appetite.

00:10:31.700 --> 00:10:32.360
Zhu Helai.

00:10:33.440 --> 00:10:34.960
Are you back with the task force?

00:10:35.200 --> 00:10:36.580
You went to catch Meng Guangcai?

00:10:37.000 --> 00:10:38.580
No, I'm just giving them some advice.

00:10:38.700 --> 00:10:40.879
Don't lie to me. Think I don't know?

00:10:40.879 --> 00:10:42.320
Then why did Xue Qin come?

00:10:42.320 --> 00:10:42.960
Huifen.

00:10:43.200 --> 00:10:43.980
Stop that.

00:10:45.500 --> 00:10:47.120
Don't you know you're sick?

00:10:47.120 --> 00:10:48.840
Don't you know your own condition?

00:10:49.480 --> 00:10:52.220
Did those punks pick a fight with you
because of this?

00:10:52.220 --> 00:10:53.639
Is it related to this?

00:10:53.639 --> 00:10:55.519
- Huifen.
- Are you out of your mind?

00:10:56.620 --> 00:10:58.759
No, I absolutely disagree with this.

00:10:58.759 --> 00:11:00.960
I need to talk to Liu Hua. You...

00:11:24.256 --> 00:11:26.973
(Time of the incident)

00:11:45.888 --> 00:11:49.056
(The 6.10 Rural Credit Union Robbery)

00:12:10.820 --> 00:12:11.360
Officer Zhu.

00:12:11.500 --> 00:12:12.200
Officer Zhu!

00:12:12.200 --> 00:12:12.860
He.

00:12:13.019 --> 00:12:13.940
Hello, Officer Zhu!

00:12:14.960 --> 00:12:15.720
Knife.

00:12:15.720 --> 00:12:17.220
Drink it, or I'm leaving.

00:12:17.820 --> 00:12:18.440
Knife.

00:12:18.440 --> 00:12:18.940
Come on.

00:12:19.379 --> 00:12:19.960
Li.

00:12:19.960 --> 00:12:20.620
Knife.

00:12:21.440 --> 00:12:22.340
What's with him now?

00:12:22.700 --> 00:12:23.460
Officer Zhu.

00:12:23.460 --> 00:12:25.600
His condition has worsened lately.

00:12:25.600 --> 00:12:26.759
He won't eat or drink.

00:12:27.519 --> 00:12:28.080
Knife.

00:12:28.080 --> 00:12:29.460
Well, I'll handle it. You can go.

00:12:29.460 --> 00:12:29.960
Okay.

00:12:30.519 --> 00:12:31.460
Hello, Officer Zhu!

00:12:32.960 --> 00:12:33.820
Hello, Officer Zhu!

00:12:35.019 --> 00:12:37.320
Hello, Officer Zhu!

00:12:37.620 --> 00:12:38.580
Hello, Officer Zhu!

00:12:39.259 --> 00:12:41.580
Xu Ming, it's me, Zhu.

00:12:42.720 --> 00:12:43.379
Zhu.

00:12:44.720 --> 00:12:45.759
We caught the bad guys.

00:12:46.379 --> 00:12:47.960
It's okay, you're safe now. Come on.

00:12:48.460 --> 00:12:49.019
Come on.

00:12:51.240 --> 00:12:51.740
Come on.

00:12:52.580 --> 00:12:53.700
Don't be afraid, come out.

00:12:55.759 --> 00:12:56.379
Sit here.

00:12:59.500 --> 00:13:00.519
The nurse just told me

00:13:01.700 --> 00:13:03.500
you haven't been
eating well lately, right?

00:13:03.500 --> 00:13:04.120
Knife.

00:13:04.620 --> 00:13:06.960
If you don't eat properly,
I won't come next time.

00:13:07.639 --> 00:13:10.019
Here, take a bite. Be good.

00:13:11.500 --> 00:13:12.460
You're being a good boy.

00:13:13.220 --> 00:13:14.240
I came today

00:13:15.580 --> 00:13:17.120
to let you help me identify someone.

00:13:19.620 --> 00:13:20.600
Take a look at this.

00:13:22.100 --> 00:13:22.740
Do you

00:13:24.360 --> 00:13:25.240
recognize this person?

00:13:28.639 --> 00:13:30.720
Knife.

00:13:31.759 --> 00:13:32.259
Knife.

00:13:33.720 --> 00:13:35.480
Take a careful look, Xu Ming.

00:13:35.519 --> 00:13:36.139
Knife.

00:13:37.500 --> 00:13:38.000
Knife.

00:13:40.840 --> 00:13:41.460
Xu Ming.

00:13:41.620 --> 00:13:42.259
Knife.

00:13:43.259 --> 00:13:45.860
All these years,
and all you can say is "knife".

00:13:45.860 --> 00:13:47.200
Can you say something more?

00:13:47.200 --> 00:13:47.759
Knife.

00:13:47.759 --> 00:13:49.139
Give me some other clue.

00:13:49.139 --> 00:13:50.639
- What knife? How long?
- Knife.

00:13:50.639 --> 00:13:51.200
Think it over.

00:13:51.200 --> 00:13:55.000
Knife...

00:13:56.340 --> 00:13:59.340
Knife...

00:13:59.340 --> 00:14:01.840
(Crack down on crime.
Protect the people.)

00:14:01.840 --> 00:14:04.940
Chief Liu, I'd like to request
extension of the investigation period.

00:14:05.080 --> 00:14:06.720
Put him under residential surveillance.

00:14:11.440 --> 00:14:13.460
I know you're under a lot of pressure.

00:14:13.759 --> 00:14:16.620
But I still hope
you can give us more support.

00:14:18.220 --> 00:14:18.980
Okay.

00:14:20.720 --> 00:14:21.860
But I have one condition.

00:14:22.460 --> 00:14:23.480
Chief Liu, go ahead.

00:14:27.259 --> 00:14:29.080
Transfer Zhu Helai away
from the task force.

00:14:32.379 --> 00:14:34.879
Chief Liu, you said it yourself.

00:14:35.019 --> 00:14:37.620
He's the one here
who knows this case best.

00:14:37.960 --> 00:14:40.100
You agreed to have him assist
with the investigation.

00:14:40.320 --> 00:14:42.100
How do you change your mind now?

00:14:42.960 --> 00:14:45.460
Transferring him out is to protect him.

00:14:47.759 --> 00:14:48.440
Chief Liu.

00:14:48.960 --> 00:14:53.100
Don't you know whether the rumors online
and in the papers are true or not?

00:14:53.960 --> 00:14:54.620
Captain Zhang.

00:14:56.200 --> 00:14:59.600
Stop considering yourself
as Zhu Helai's apprentice.

00:15:00.320 --> 00:15:01.879
You're also a police officer.

00:15:06.460 --> 00:15:07.120
Chief Liu.

00:15:09.620 --> 00:15:10.480
Captain Zhang.

00:15:11.460 --> 00:15:12.220
Master.

00:15:18.600 --> 00:15:19.240
Chief Liu.

00:15:22.000 --> 00:15:22.820
Chief Liu.

00:15:29.240 --> 00:15:29.980
Liu Hua.

00:15:42.960 --> 00:15:43.879
What do you want?

00:15:43.879 --> 00:15:46.879
About the task force to extend
the investigation period for Guangcai...

00:15:46.879 --> 00:15:47.620
I approved it.

00:15:47.620 --> 00:15:51.000
You approved it? Then why did
Zhang Wei leave looking so down?

00:15:51.580 --> 00:15:53.620
- Transfer you away from the task force.
- Why?

00:15:53.620 --> 00:15:54.519
You tell me why?

00:15:55.580 --> 00:15:56.980
Look at the rumors online

00:15:58.100 --> 00:15:59.480
about this 6.10 case.

00:16:01.139 --> 00:16:03.392
Know what they say about you?
Seeking personal revenge.

00:16:03.720 --> 00:16:05.100
We got a report last night.

00:16:05.100 --> 00:16:06.000
What did you do?

00:16:07.320 --> 00:16:08.340
You fought on the street?

00:16:08.960 --> 00:16:09.879
What do you want?

00:16:10.100 --> 00:16:11.519
You're endangering our image.

00:16:12.320 --> 00:16:15.000
Zhu, I'm telling you,
I know what kind of person you are.

00:16:15.340 --> 00:16:17.120
But others don't know.

00:16:17.120 --> 00:16:18.759
They're trying to smear me,

00:16:18.759 --> 00:16:20.940
which proves
our investigation direction is correct.

00:16:21.320 --> 00:16:23.620
They just want
to push me out of the task force.

00:16:24.200 --> 00:16:26.960
Liu Hua, you can't just call me in
and then kick me out like that.

00:16:27.220 --> 00:16:29.120
(Pre-operation mobilization meeting)
Guys, with leadership approval,

00:16:29.379 --> 00:16:32.259
(for the 6.10 case task force)
the 6.10 case task force is established.

00:16:33.200 --> 00:16:36.019
Zhang Wei will serve
as the head of the task force.

00:16:36.600 --> 00:16:40.100
Li Quanyi from Technical Unit
will serve as deputy head.

00:16:41.379 --> 00:16:42.259
And Zhu Helai

00:16:43.620 --> 00:16:45.340
had been in the Logistics Support.

00:16:45.340 --> 00:16:46.960
Today, he officially joins us.

00:16:53.000 --> 00:16:56.960
Chief Liu, I object to Officer Zhu
joining the task force.

00:16:57.940 --> 00:17:00.960
First, he's been off the front lines
of criminal investigation for long.

00:17:01.320 --> 00:17:03.940
Second, he has had contact
with suspects in the 6.10 case.

00:17:04.619 --> 00:17:08.339
Given that the 6.10 case
occurred eighteen years ago

00:17:08.440 --> 00:17:10.528
and it's been a long time,
and there are many clues,

00:17:10.619 --> 00:17:13.640
many of young colleagues
are unfamiliar with this case.

00:17:14.960 --> 00:17:17.559
Zhu Helai knows this case best.

00:17:17.559 --> 00:17:19.819
Therefore, I've reported this
to the higher-ups.

00:17:20.140 --> 00:17:21.140
He will assist us.

00:17:26.579 --> 00:17:27.240
Fine, I'll go.

00:17:27.960 --> 00:17:28.759
Zhu, listen.

00:17:28.759 --> 00:17:32.240
We've been old classmates
for thirty years. Thirty years!

00:17:32.559 --> 00:17:34.720
Who has a closer bond than us here?

00:17:34.960 --> 00:17:36.128
When housing was allocated,

00:17:36.259 --> 00:17:39.380
people were lining up at your door,
desperate to get in.

00:17:39.720 --> 00:17:41.380
Did I ever come?

00:17:41.500 --> 00:17:43.579
Did I ever use our bond to come?

00:17:43.579 --> 00:17:46.319
Five years ago, when I was assigned
to the cafeteria, did I come?

00:17:46.319 --> 00:17:49.220
With your conscience,
Liu Unity, think about it.

00:17:56.099 --> 00:17:58.380
Sit, Zhu, sit.

00:18:06.740 --> 00:18:07.880
Zhu.

00:18:08.460 --> 00:18:09.720
You've been tied to this case

00:18:10.500 --> 00:18:11.940
for too many years.

00:18:14.299 --> 00:18:15.700
Transferring you out

00:18:17.000 --> 00:18:18.319
is also to protect you.

00:18:18.319 --> 00:18:19.200
I know.

00:18:20.700 --> 00:18:21.480
But

00:18:22.799 --> 00:18:24.140
I can't let go of the 6.10 case.

00:18:27.500 --> 00:18:28.500
Just this once.

00:18:57.759 --> 00:18:59.099
Be careful of everything.

00:19:01.380 --> 00:19:02.220
Yes, Chief Liu.

00:19:02.339 --> 00:19:03.500
I will definitely be careful

00:19:03.500 --> 00:19:06.339
and catch all the criminals
under Captain Zhang and Li's leadership

00:19:06.339 --> 00:19:07.220
to settle this case.

00:19:41.380 --> 00:19:42.519
I kept the hotel room.

00:19:43.740 --> 00:19:45.759
The police will think
we're still here for now.

00:19:46.099 --> 00:19:49.099
Let's go back to Beiyan during this time
to check things out.

00:19:50.059 --> 00:19:51.440
Remember the plan we had?

00:19:54.900 --> 00:19:57.400
Lijun, don't worry.

00:19:57.799 --> 00:20:00.339
I'm not an idiot.

00:20:08.500 --> 00:20:13.220
Are you overestimating Zhu?

00:20:14.059 --> 00:20:16.839
Indeed, he was quite impressive before.

00:20:17.480 --> 00:20:19.900
But time has changed.

00:20:21.500 --> 00:20:25.019
Lijun, given our current status
and position...

00:20:25.200 --> 00:20:26.200
Right? Tell me...

00:20:32.700 --> 00:20:33.319
Wang Dazhu.

00:20:34.339 --> 00:20:36.200
What status and position
do you have now?

00:20:37.000 --> 00:20:39.000
If you still act recklessly like before,

00:20:39.059 --> 00:20:41.380
even a small mistake
could make all our efforts wasted.

00:20:43.839 --> 00:20:44.700
You remember this.

00:20:45.339 --> 00:20:46.559
No matter what happens,

00:20:47.079 --> 00:20:50.099
you must strictly follow
our previous plan. Understand?

00:20:51.700 --> 00:20:53.019
Got it.

00:20:53.599 --> 00:20:54.579
Understand?

00:20:57.519 --> 00:20:58.480
Yes.

00:21:04.500 --> 00:21:08.460
(As the city's most renowned
philanthropist and business star,)

00:21:08.460 --> 00:21:10.660
(Meng Guangcai, Chairman
of Caisheng Group, was taken away)

00:21:10.660 --> 00:21:14.940
(by police during the strategic
cooperation signing ceremony yesterday.)

00:21:15.039 --> 00:21:16.319
(As of the time of report release,)

00:21:16.319 --> 00:21:21.420
(relevant authorities haven't announced
if he's involved in criminal offenses.)

00:21:49.059 --> 00:21:49.740
Officer.

00:21:50.839 --> 00:21:51.700
I confess.

00:21:58.720 --> 00:21:59.799
Is this what you confess?

00:22:03.960 --> 00:22:05.500
I'm a law-abiding businessman.

00:22:06.519 --> 00:22:09.000
You're detaining me
with no proper reason.

00:22:09.200 --> 00:22:13.099
I suspect Zhu Helai
retaliates against me

00:22:13.099 --> 00:22:14.160
out of personal grudges.

00:22:15.140 --> 00:22:16.220
I'm filing a complaint.

00:22:17.200 --> 00:22:20.240
I'm complaining now. I demand
you to investigate him thoroughly.

00:22:21.079 --> 00:22:21.880
Meng Guangcai.

00:22:22.500 --> 00:22:25.259
You are currently
under interrogation and investigation.

00:22:25.740 --> 00:22:27.960
You're responsible
for every word you say.

00:22:31.740 --> 00:22:33.000
I'm filing a complaint.

00:22:34.319 --> 00:22:35.339
Are you shielding him?

00:22:37.599 --> 00:22:39.200
You're detaining me without reason.

00:22:39.500 --> 00:22:41.559
If anything happens to my health,

00:22:42.259 --> 00:22:43.880
you will be held responsible.

00:22:44.240 --> 00:22:45.720
He's having a breakdown, isn't he?

00:22:46.380 --> 00:22:47.808
He's still putting on an act here.

00:22:49.160 --> 00:22:51.259
He must've read
a lot of law books these years.

00:22:52.240 --> 00:22:53.900
He's practically semi-professional.

00:22:54.500 --> 00:22:57.960
When he first came in,
he wasted time chit-chatting with me.

00:22:58.500 --> 00:23:00.980
Now it's been twenty-four hours
and he hasn't been released.

00:23:01.900 --> 00:23:03.440
He's forcing us to show our evidence.

00:23:06.019 --> 00:23:08.640
Captain Li, stop holding back.
Play your cards.

00:23:10.000 --> 00:23:11.339
So you're worked up

00:23:11.339 --> 00:23:13.799
just to find out
about the evidence, isn't it?

00:23:14.339 --> 00:23:15.240
I can tell you.

00:23:16.140 --> 00:23:17.799
Evidence related to you was found

00:23:18.880 --> 00:23:20.480
at the scene of the 6.10 case.

00:23:30.240 --> 00:23:32.500
Evidence related to me?

00:23:34.299 --> 00:23:35.460
If you had evidence,

00:23:35.960 --> 00:23:37.740
would Zhu Helai only arrest me today?

00:23:38.900 --> 00:23:40.000
If you had evidence,

00:23:40.339 --> 00:23:42.519
would you still be
beating around the bush here?

00:23:43.579 --> 00:23:45.819
I suspect you're bluffing me.

00:23:49.160 --> 00:23:51.099
When will his blood test result be out?

00:23:51.240 --> 00:23:53.220
The official report
will still take a few days.

00:23:54.000 --> 00:23:56.200
Even when the report's out,
we can't show it to him.

00:23:56.519 --> 00:23:57.880
We need him to confess himself.

00:23:58.000 --> 00:24:00.380
He doesn't know what evidence we have.

00:24:00.380 --> 00:24:01.380
He's clinging to hope.

00:24:02.480 --> 00:24:03.599
After all these years,

00:24:04.519 --> 00:24:06.799
you're still fixated on this case.

00:24:10.380 --> 00:24:12.220
Since you care so much about this case,

00:24:13.000 --> 00:24:16.599
as a law-abiding citizen,
I can do my duty

00:24:17.259 --> 00:24:18.819
and provide you with some leads.

00:24:20.400 --> 00:24:23.240
Didn't you hear those rumors back then?

00:24:26.579 --> 00:24:28.339
Rumors? What rumors?

00:24:30.200 --> 00:24:32.220
After the robbery in 1993,

00:24:33.200 --> 00:24:35.579
Beiyan newspapers
were flooded with reports.

00:24:37.019 --> 00:24:40.319
Wanted posters were plastered
all over the streets.

00:24:41.299 --> 00:24:43.160
You police kept questioning people.

00:24:43.839 --> 00:24:46.500
The entire construction site
was thrown into chaos.

00:24:47.500 --> 00:24:49.079
Actually, people back then speculated

00:24:49.819 --> 00:24:51.240
that under such intense situation,

00:24:53.000 --> 00:24:55.839
anyone went missing at that time

00:24:56.440 --> 00:24:58.440
must be related to the robbery.

00:25:01.720 --> 00:25:04.599
And as expected,
two people went missing.

00:25:06.599 --> 00:25:07.579
Both were locals.

00:25:08.079 --> 00:25:11.160
One was named Zuo Long,
the other one was Ma Zhongwu.

00:25:18.000 --> 00:25:19.700
Haven't you heard that rumor?

00:25:22.519 --> 00:25:26.640
So you're confessing your accomplices
to seek leniency, aren't you?

00:25:27.460 --> 00:25:28.599
Let me reiterate.

00:25:29.000 --> 00:25:31.640
I have nothing to do with the robbery.

00:25:32.900 --> 00:25:36.160
We've had files on both individuals
mentioned by Meng Guangcai.

00:25:36.740 --> 00:25:40.740
Zuo Long, male,
born in Xiguan Town in 1957.

00:25:41.220 --> 00:25:43.819
(The 6.10 City Credit Union Robbery)
Later he settled in Shaguai Village,

00:25:43.980 --> 00:25:45.519
Magou Town, running a mining plant.

00:25:46.339 --> 00:25:48.519
He was sent to reform
for two years in 1989,

00:25:48.519 --> 00:25:50.819
and then he disappeared
after release in Beiyan in 1991.

00:25:51.519 --> 00:25:53.599
If involved in the robbery,
he was 36 years old then.

00:25:54.880 --> 00:25:58.599
Ma Zhongwu, male, born in 1964.

00:25:59.000 --> 00:26:01.024
His parents worked
for Beiyan Machinery Factory.

00:26:01.460 --> 00:26:04.220
Fired from the factory in 1991
for intentional assault,

00:26:04.519 --> 00:26:06.460
he disappeared after 1993.

00:26:06.880 --> 00:26:09.500
If involved in the robbery,
he was 29 years old then.

00:26:10.140 --> 00:26:11.740
According to eyewitness testimony,

00:26:12.400 --> 00:26:14.079
there were three robbers at the scene.

00:26:14.579 --> 00:26:18.140
Could it be Zuo Long,
Ma Zhongwu, and Meng Guangcai?

00:26:18.539 --> 00:26:21.200
Meng Guangcai refused to admit
he was involved in the robbery,

00:26:22.700 --> 00:26:25.099
and even threw out
a smokescreen to test us.

00:26:26.500 --> 00:26:28.000
That just shows he's guilty.

00:26:28.740 --> 00:26:31.819
He had another purpose
for throwing out that smokescreen.

00:26:33.259 --> 00:26:35.839
It was to cover for other suspects.

00:26:35.839 --> 00:26:38.099
Jiao Lijun and Wang Dazhu
had followed him around.

00:26:39.140 --> 00:26:40.380
If they weren't involved,

00:26:41.740 --> 00:26:42.640
I wouldn't buy it.

00:26:43.740 --> 00:26:46.519
Rest assured. Both Jiao Lijun
and Wang Dazhu are under watch,

00:26:46.519 --> 00:26:47.392
and won't get away.

00:26:47.579 --> 00:26:49.819
But we can't let our guard down
with the list

00:26:50.160 --> 00:26:51.720
the suspect provided.

00:26:52.440 --> 00:26:55.000
You've been investigating
this case since 1993.

00:26:55.140 --> 00:26:57.059
Any rumors back then?

00:26:58.000 --> 00:27:00.460
Ma Zhongwu was
a well-known troublemaker back then.

00:27:01.059 --> 00:27:02.460
Lots of rumors about him.

00:27:03.160 --> 00:27:04.240
And when Zuo Long

00:27:05.599 --> 00:27:06.759
went missing,

00:27:08.000 --> 00:27:09.000
I looked into it too.

00:27:10.944 --> 00:27:14.286
(Police Station in Magou Town,
Beiyan County, 1991)

00:27:15.240 --> 00:27:16.240
Stop crying.

00:27:18.000 --> 00:27:19.839
Why did the police call us here?

00:27:19.839 --> 00:27:20.759
Help find him.

00:27:22.339 --> 00:27:24.900
We've been looking for months
and haven't found him.

00:27:25.440 --> 00:27:28.220
That's why they called us here.
Stop crying.

00:27:28.599 --> 00:27:30.839
How could he just disappear like that?

00:27:30.839 --> 00:27:33.240
They'll help us. Don't cry.

00:27:33.579 --> 00:27:36.960
Officer, you have to help us find him.

00:27:37.059 --> 00:27:38.000
(Zuo Long's wife)
Stop crying.

00:27:38.000 --> 00:27:39.940
(Zuo Long's brother-in-law)
He's not dead. Why are you crying?

00:27:41.700 --> 00:27:43.000
You're that Zhu guy?

00:27:45.019 --> 00:27:46.259
I'm Zhu Helai. What is it?

00:27:46.940 --> 00:27:47.720
Officer.

00:27:47.720 --> 00:27:48.299
Alright.

00:27:49.980 --> 00:27:52.096
Zuo Long disappeared
after leaving the police station.

00:27:52.460 --> 00:27:54.940
He never came home. You're responsible.

00:27:55.720 --> 00:27:57.099
After he went missing,

00:27:57.099 --> 00:27:59.000
we've been searching
since we got the report.

00:27:59.000 --> 00:28:00.960
We'll notify you of any updates.

00:28:01.599 --> 00:28:02.500
Calm down!

00:28:03.700 --> 00:28:05.960
He said he had a grudge against you.

00:28:08.579 --> 00:28:10.599
Did he contact you before disappearing?

00:28:12.000 --> 00:28:13.099
Alright.

00:28:14.000 --> 00:28:15.700
That's a pointless question!

00:28:15.700 --> 00:28:18.220
If he contacted us,
why did we have to come here?

00:28:19.200 --> 00:28:21.380
Besides, finding people is your job.

00:28:21.380 --> 00:28:23.660
I'm speaking with Zuo Long's
immediate family right now.

00:28:23.799 --> 00:28:24.740
Could you step aside?

00:28:24.819 --> 00:28:25.640
What did you say?

00:28:29.579 --> 00:28:31.500
He said he knew you.

00:28:31.500 --> 00:28:35.400
You locked him up
to get revenge for your subordinate.

00:28:36.000 --> 00:28:38.160
I'm warning you, watch your language.

00:28:38.160 --> 00:28:39.200
Language?

00:28:39.480 --> 00:28:41.160
Come on. Lock me up too.

00:28:41.160 --> 00:28:43.019
Lock me up.

00:28:43.740 --> 00:28:45.660
Brother, what are you doing?

00:28:46.700 --> 00:28:47.700
Listen.

00:28:48.940 --> 00:28:51.200
You will take full responsibility
for his disappearance.

00:28:51.200 --> 00:28:52.099
You're accountable.

00:28:52.099 --> 00:28:54.599
No matter he is alive or dead,
bring him to us.

00:28:54.900 --> 00:28:55.799
Understand?

00:28:55.799 --> 00:28:56.579
By the way,

00:28:57.400 --> 00:28:59.220
about his mine.

00:28:59.460 --> 00:29:01.339
You owe us an explanation!
Give us an answer!

00:29:01.339 --> 00:29:02.400
- This is a police station.
- Heard me?

00:29:02.400 --> 00:29:03.240
Watch your behavior.

00:29:06.400 --> 00:29:08.339
Police's hitting me!

00:29:08.799 --> 00:29:10.140
Police's hitting me!

00:29:10.140 --> 00:29:11.500
- What's wrong?
- Police's hitting me!

00:29:11.500 --> 00:29:12.200
What's wrong, Zhu?

00:29:12.200 --> 00:29:15.160
Police's hitting me!

00:29:16.019 --> 00:29:18.200
Zhu, this guy is troublesome.

00:29:18.339 --> 00:29:19.460
Go ahead, I'll handle this.

00:29:19.460 --> 00:29:22.259
You just got transferred.
Don't let this affect you. Go.

00:29:22.259 --> 00:29:24.160
Police's hitting me!

00:29:25.000 --> 00:29:26.500
Police's hitting me!

00:29:28.140 --> 00:29:30.519
Yang Banzui,
you don't even recognize me?

00:29:31.200 --> 00:29:31.839
Get up!

00:29:33.500 --> 00:29:34.319
You hear me?

00:29:35.059 --> 00:29:37.339
Yang Erwan, get up!

00:29:39.339 --> 00:29:41.400
I'll get up, so what?

00:29:41.400 --> 00:29:43.019
What? Is this your house?

00:29:43.460 --> 00:29:44.579
This is a police station.

00:29:44.579 --> 00:29:45.259
So what?

00:29:45.259 --> 00:29:46.839
I'm a frequent visitor here.

00:29:46.839 --> 00:29:47.940
Let me tell you.

00:29:47.940 --> 00:29:50.640
Don't mess around
with such a hairstyle and flashy shirt.

00:29:50.640 --> 00:29:52.720
Stand properly! You hear me?

00:30:04.992 --> 00:30:07.740
(Century Video Theater)

00:30:07.740 --> 00:30:08.480
Come again.

00:30:08.500 --> 00:30:09.200
Alright.

00:30:14.240 --> 00:30:14.980
Qin.

00:30:16.259 --> 00:30:17.519
Zhu, what brings you here?

00:30:17.960 --> 00:30:20.140
I saw quite a few people
coming and going.

00:30:20.500 --> 00:30:21.400
Business seems good.

00:30:22.400 --> 00:30:24.000
But it doesn't concern me.

00:30:24.000 --> 00:30:24.900
I'm just working here.

00:30:25.400 --> 00:30:27.880
Qin, Guangcai is working in Beiyan.

00:30:28.299 --> 00:30:30.740
You have to take care
of Yonghui and Principal Chen.

00:30:31.740 --> 00:30:32.740
How heavy a burden.

00:30:33.000 --> 00:30:35.140
Listen to me. Don't reject me.

00:30:35.140 --> 00:30:36.400
Take this money.

00:30:36.400 --> 00:30:37.500
I can't take it, Zhu.

00:30:37.799 --> 00:30:39.000
You're living a hard time.

00:30:39.000 --> 00:30:39.839
With meager wage,

00:30:39.839 --> 00:30:41.339
you can't keep helping us out.

00:30:41.339 --> 00:30:42.339
Don't reject me.

00:30:42.339 --> 00:30:44.500
Right now, I have enough money to use.

00:30:44.799 --> 00:30:46.960
When you're better off
and making it big,

00:30:47.140 --> 00:30:48.640
then you pay me back. Just take it.

00:30:49.500 --> 00:30:51.519
Don't reject me. Take it.

00:30:51.740 --> 00:30:52.599
Sit, Zhu.

00:30:53.400 --> 00:30:55.140
Out of water here.
I'll get you some water.

00:30:56.900 --> 00:30:58.839
Qin.

00:30:59.460 --> 00:31:02.140
Don't bother. I just have
a couple of questions for you.

00:31:02.140 --> 00:31:03.599
What is it, Zhu?

00:31:03.599 --> 00:31:04.140
Sit here.

00:31:04.140 --> 00:31:05.000
Have some water.

00:31:05.000 --> 00:31:05.799
Sit here.

00:31:05.960 --> 00:31:06.660
No rush.

00:31:07.400 --> 00:31:09.019
Just some questions, then I'll be off.

00:31:11.240 --> 00:31:12.519
Have some water. It's raining.

00:31:12.759 --> 00:31:13.259
Qin.

00:31:15.339 --> 00:31:18.440
When was the last time you saw Zuo Long?

00:31:26.019 --> 00:31:29.740
I haven't seen him since you sent him
off for reform through labor.

00:31:32.720 --> 00:31:33.480
Qin.

00:31:33.480 --> 00:31:37.000
You see a lot of people here, so you
must hear more news than I do.

00:31:37.599 --> 00:31:40.940
Have you heard anyone
talking about Zuo Long's disappearance?

00:31:42.519 --> 00:31:44.099
Take your time. Think it over.

00:31:44.799 --> 00:31:46.000
Tell me if you heard anything.

00:31:54.700 --> 00:31:56.000
I don't want him missing.

00:32:00.000 --> 00:32:01.259
I want him dead.

00:32:06.500 --> 00:32:09.720
You, teach them how ticks crawl.

00:32:10.160 --> 00:32:12.319
Crawl over there.
Then I'll let them all go.

00:32:12.319 --> 00:32:13.339
Hurry up.

00:32:15.779 --> 00:32:16.500
Hurry up.

00:32:27.000 --> 00:32:28.220
I want him dead.

00:32:33.740 --> 00:32:34.240
Qin.

00:32:34.240 --> 00:32:36.019
Zhu, I don't want
to talk about him anymore.

00:32:36.599 --> 00:32:37.819
You should ask someone else.

00:32:43.460 --> 00:32:45.240
The fact that you couldn't find out

00:32:45.640 --> 00:32:47.420
doesn't mean we can't find out now.

00:32:49.019 --> 00:32:50.400
Now that Ma Zhongwu

00:32:51.059 --> 00:32:52.559
was involved in the rumors back then.

00:32:52.799 --> 00:32:54.960
Zuo Long and Meng Guangcai
were from the same hometown.

00:32:55.240 --> 00:32:57.339
Then the credibility
of this lead is very high.

00:32:57.980 --> 00:33:00.200
What now? Just let it sit?

00:33:00.740 --> 00:33:01.500
No investigation?

00:33:02.000 --> 00:33:04.900
Wait, Captain Li, don't rush.

00:33:04.900 --> 00:33:07.400
No matter how the case
was investigated back then,

00:33:07.640 --> 00:33:09.819
re-investigation won't hurt.

00:33:11.259 --> 00:33:13.839
Keep a close watch on Wang and Jiao.

00:33:13.839 --> 00:33:15.259
And Zuo and Ma can't be overlooked.

00:33:15.259 --> 00:33:18.200
Well, Captain Li, you take
Liang to Shaguai Village.

00:33:18.200 --> 00:33:18.700
Yes.

00:33:18.799 --> 00:33:20.319
Zhou, you come with me.

00:33:21.000 --> 00:33:22.400
Get ready. Let's head out.

00:33:36.000 --> 00:33:37.740
- Excuse me, police.
- Hello.

00:33:37.740 --> 00:33:38.720
- Hello.
- Hello.

00:33:38.720 --> 00:33:39.900
Is this Building 6, Unit 2?

00:33:39.980 --> 00:33:40.480
Yes.

00:33:40.740 --> 00:33:42.000
We'd like to know something.

00:33:42.960 --> 00:33:43.980
Have you seen this man?

00:33:45.660 --> 00:33:46.460
Hello.

00:33:48.519 --> 00:33:51.099
Hello, ma'am.
Are you Ma Zhongwu's mother?

00:33:51.980 --> 00:33:53.000
That's Zuo Long.

00:33:53.000 --> 00:33:53.640
You know him?

00:33:53.640 --> 00:33:54.400
Yes, I know him.

00:33:54.400 --> 00:33:55.648
Have you seen him recently?

00:33:55.819 --> 00:33:56.319
No.

00:33:56.319 --> 00:33:58.240
- He hasn't been back for long.
- When was the last time you saw him?

00:33:58.839 --> 00:34:00.339
Too long ago, I don't remember.

00:34:00.339 --> 00:34:00.980
Thanks.

00:34:01.740 --> 00:34:03.460
Ma'am, no need to see us out.

00:34:03.460 --> 00:34:06.339
Thanks for your cooperation.
We might need to come again.

00:34:06.500 --> 00:34:07.160
Alright.

00:34:19.400 --> 00:34:22.000
Dazhu, the police came looking
for Ma Zhongwu's mom.

00:34:59.539 --> 00:35:00.340
(1991)
Principal Chen.

00:35:02.059 --> 00:35:02.940
Zhu.

00:35:03.340 --> 00:35:04.579
Mr. Chen, Officer Zhu is here.

00:35:05.460 --> 00:35:06.139
Please sit.

00:35:06.139 --> 00:35:08.440
Officer Zhu, come.

00:35:08.440 --> 00:35:09.480
- Just sit.
- Don't bother.

00:35:09.480 --> 00:35:10.559
I just came to see you.

00:35:12.300 --> 00:35:14.980
Since you moved to town,
I haven't been able to visit much.

00:35:15.539 --> 00:35:17.179
When I go to Beiyan later,

00:35:17.480 --> 00:35:18.960
I'll have even less time to visit.

00:35:19.579 --> 00:35:22.300
Officer Zhu, you're too polite.

00:35:22.900 --> 00:35:27.360
I know you've always been
helping Guangcai out.

00:35:27.360 --> 00:35:28.099
It's only right.

00:35:28.460 --> 00:35:31.340
You care for him
like your own younger brother.

00:35:31.480 --> 00:35:32.480
Zhu, have some water.

00:35:33.340 --> 00:35:34.179
Thanks, Yonghui.

00:35:35.320 --> 00:35:36.000
Principal Chen.

00:35:36.860 --> 00:35:41.780
I came to ask you about Zuo Long.

00:35:41.980 --> 00:35:44.500
Do you have any records here?

00:35:46.400 --> 00:35:47.639
Just a moment.

00:35:49.019 --> 00:35:49.840
Take your time.

00:36:02.960 --> 00:36:05.760
I'll do it. I'll look through it myself.

00:36:11.119 --> 00:36:12.059
Last year,

00:36:12.760 --> 00:36:15.079
I was still the security director.

00:36:15.599 --> 00:36:16.539
I recorded everything.

00:36:16.539 --> 00:36:17.800
Yes, I know.

00:36:17.800 --> 00:36:18.699
But Principal Chen,

00:36:19.780 --> 00:36:23.519
you should get your eyes checked.

00:36:23.639 --> 00:36:24.860
Don't delay it.

00:36:25.360 --> 00:36:29.179
I'm truly holding Guangcai back.

00:36:30.980 --> 00:36:34.460
Since my eyesight worsened,

00:36:35.179 --> 00:36:37.780
he has insisted on bringing me to town.

00:36:38.000 --> 00:36:40.599
He went to work at construction sites
to earn money

00:36:41.340 --> 00:36:45.760
and had Qin stay to care for me.

00:36:47.840 --> 00:36:50.099
When I mentioned Zuo Long to Qin,

00:36:50.099 --> 00:36:51.880
she was still emotionally unstable.

00:36:54.480 --> 00:36:57.280
After Zuo Long harassed her last time,

00:36:57.400 --> 00:37:01.039
she's kept all her pain bottled up.

00:37:02.719 --> 00:37:07.340
But villagers love to gossip.

00:37:08.440 --> 00:37:09.780
Though she didn't complain,

00:37:10.280 --> 00:37:11.840
with those people there,

00:37:12.019 --> 00:37:16.699
Qin has to remain in this town.

00:37:19.619 --> 00:37:23.159
We avoid mentioning it around her.

00:37:29.121 --> 00:37:34.145
=The Silent Rift=